### ============================================================================
### KTC ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### Refresh all KTC data (dynasty + redraft, all formats and TEP levels)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/refresh/all 

### Refresh KTC rankings (specific configuration - dynasty superflex TEP)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/refresh?tep_level=tep&is_redraft=false&league_format=superflex

### Refresh KTC rankings (dynasty 1QB with TEP)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/refresh?tep_level=tep&is_redraft=false&league_format=1qb

### Refresh KTC rankings (redraft superflex)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/refresh?tep_level=&is_redraft=true&league_format=superflex



### *** Get KTC rankings (dynasty superflex with TEP) ***
GET http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/rankings?tep_level=tep&is_redraft=false&league_format=superflex

### Get KTC rankings (dynasty 1QB with TEP)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/rankings?tep_level=tep&is_redraft=false&league_format=1qb

### Get KTC rankings (redraft superflex)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/rankings?tep_level=&is_redraft=true&league_format=superflex

### Get KTC rankings (dynasty 1QB base)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/rankings?tep_level=&is_redraft=false&league_format=1qb

### ============================================================================
### Cleanup KTC database
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ktc/cleanup?tep_level=tep&is_redraft=false&league_format=superflex

